MacroHedgeStrategist::lifecycle
├── when requestSchoolDecision is called with a known dataKey
│   ├── it reads the oracle scaledValue as actual
│   ├── it allocates a fresh decisionId from the school requestId
│   ├── it sends an inferString school payload to the LLM agent id with the registry school labels
│   └── it marks the school requestId pending and emits HedgeDecisionRequested
├── when requestSchoolDecision is called with an unknown dataKey
│   └── it should revert UnknownKey
├── when requestNotionalDecision is called with a known decisionId whose school callback has completed
│   ├── it sends an inferNumber notional payload to the LLM agent id
│   └── it binds the notional requestId to the same decisionId
├── when requestNotionalDecision is called and the decision is not ready
│   ├── given the decisionId is unknown
│   │   └── it should revert UnknownDecision
│   ├── given the school callback has not completed
│   │   └── it should revert UnknownDecision
│   └── given the notional leg already completed
│       └── it should revert UnknownDecision
├── when the school callback arrives from the platform
│   ├── given the school string maps to a registry label
│   │   └── it stores the school handle and sets schoolSet true
│   ├── given the school string does not map to any registry label
│   │   └── it emits DecisionFailed and leaves schoolSet false and not fire StrategistDecided
│   └── given the school payload is an int encoded thirty two byte blob
│       └── it emits DecisionFailed and leaves schoolSet false
├── when the notional callback arrives from the platform after the school leg completed
│   ├── given the notional is strictly within MIN_NOTIONAL and MAX_NOTIONAL
│   │   └── it stores the notional unchanged
│   ├── given the notional exceeds MAX_NOTIONAL
│   │   └── it clamps the stored notional to MAX_NOTIONAL
│   ├── given the notional raw is positive but below MIN_NOTIONAL
│   │   └── it floors the stored notional up to MIN_NOTIONAL
│   ├── given the notional raw int is negative
│   │   └── it floors the stored notional to MIN_NOTIONAL
│   └── given the notional payload is not thirty two bytes
│       └── it emits DecisionFailed and leaves notionalSet false
├── when both school and notional callbacks have arrived on the same decisionId
│   ├── it emits StrategistDecided with the decisionId school and mandate
│   └── given the two callbacks land in different blocks
│       └── it should still emit StrategistDecided
├── when a mandate is assembled
│   ├── it anchors underlyingMarket to the polygon wcop usdc pool id
│   ├── it resolves the school handle to a non zero thesis
│   ├── it bounds the target notional in range
│   ├── it sets chainId to 137 and isLong true
│   └── it lines up the mandate field types with the hedge leg params hand off
└── when a callback caller is not the platform
    ├── it should revert NotPlatform
    └── given an unknown or replayed requestId
        └── it should revert UnknownRequest
